// XPath
I.click('//form/*[@type=submit]');
// link in context
I.click('Logout', '#nav');
// using strict locator
I.click({css: 'nav a.login'});  Parameters   locator   clickable link or button located by text, or any element located by CSS|XPath|strict locator  button     context   (optional) element to search in CSS|XPath|Strict locator

